AUTOTOOLS HELLOWORLD
========================
Before to build this project, you should have your autoconf and automake installed. You may obtain it using these commands:

$ wget https://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/autoconf/autoconf-latest.tar.gz
$ wget https://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/automake/automake-1.15.1.tar.gz

To build configure script, using the following steps:

$ aclocal
$ automake --add-missing
$ autoheader
$ autoconf

To build the whole project, using the following:

$ ./configure
$ make
$ make install

Also, you can archive this project using `make dist'

